title: Eetcafe Eureka
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Every Wednesday the restaurant is vegetarian only, of which some might be vegan. Every fourth Wednesday of the month is vegan menu. Check website for weekly menu. Reserve in advance (before 4pm). Eureka is a social and cultural association, situated in an old building just outside the center of the city. Founded in 1992, hosts many cultural and social initiatives and is run by volunteers.
